    • Method Detail

      • onLoaded

        List<ChunkTicketManager.LoadingTicket> onLoaded(ImmutableList<ChunkTicketManager.LoadingTicket> tickets,
                                                World world,
                                                int maxTickets)
        Callback for loading Tickets during world load.

        During this callback you cannot associate chunks to tickets. This callback gets all loaded non-player tickets. The returned list will be truncated to maxTickets after this callback is called, and and tickets absent from the list will be released.

        Parameters:
        tickets - The list of loaded tickets
        world - The world tickets were loaded for
        maxTickets - The maximum tickets allowed for this plugin
        Returns:
        A list of all tickets you wish to keep
